{"tid":254971,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本單車遊記","createTime":"2017-05-23T14:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T01:51:14.000Z","uid":118241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce2bf8d063990dcb699f63652ed64e46a9cac74","tid":254971,"uid":118241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"大家好 小弟係岩岩果一個月同fd去左日本踩單車 由福岡去札幌(原本plan係福岡去宗谷岬(日本最北) 不過中途嘅意外 最後不停轉plan 好彩最後都去到札幌完成行程<br />\n<br />\n交待一下背景先 小弟26歲 自從年半前去左台灣環島之後 就愛上左單車旅行 係香港都會係馬路踩下單車 不過就唔多<br />\n友人都去過台灣環島(唔係一齊去) 係香港好少踩單車 不過為左今次旅程就買左部小輪徑<br />\n係2016年9月果時 我隨口問左一句 不如去日本踩單車 順便探下友人2(友人2係香港人但係日本工作 長住日本) 友人一句好啊 就展開左我哋日本之旅<br />\n我當時岩岩做完十字韌帶手術 喺屋企冇嘢做養傷個時就喺度搵吓資料 因為我哋對日本真係一曉不通<br />\n<br />\n小弟打得慢 同埋仲執緊相 出得慢希望大家多多包涵 儘量做到多圖多字"},{"pid":"16eb5448bb9580b5dcfe149ed1b7c0d4650d862c","tid":254971,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8f6568d9c2e389d46d516a8ce3a3593f23d9f8","tid":254971,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"abd3a37f56ba3ddc097bbd32215d3451a4b9f17b","tid":254971,"uid":118241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"我地原本個planning<br />\nDay 1 福岡去北九州(過埋去本州)<br />\n2 北九州去岩國<br />\n3 岩國去四國今治 (廣島港搭船去埋松山再踩去今治)<br />\n4 今治去岡山<br />\n5 岡山去神戶 (買咗飛當晚六點睇棒球)<br />\n6 神户去甲賀<br />\n7 甲賀去名古屋 (名古屋搵日本朋友一齊踩去東京)<br />\n8 名古屋去磐田<br />\n9 磐田去富士<br />\n10 富士去小田原<br />\n11 小田原去東京<br />\n之後東京休息三日<br />\n14 東京去宇都宮<br />\n15 宇都宮去福島<br />\n16 福島去仙台<br />\n17 仙台去平泉<br />\n18 平泉去盛岡<br />\n19 盛岡去八户<br />\n20 八戶去青森<br />\n21  青森去八雲町<br />\n22 八雲町去登別<br />\n23 登別去札幌<br />\n24 札幌去稚內<br />\n25稚內再去上日本最北<br />\n<br />\n不過踩完第一日已經知跟唔到planning 因為成個trip太多意外發生"},{"pid":"dfd4439c42cd89b0cdcdaa56bd5ebc9cbbcebfca","tid":254971,"uid":26302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5d1237c5fc9fd01a331001b9cf9098c816afe4dc","tid":254971,"uid":118241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"準備篇<br />\n出發前一個月已經周圍揾單車店買紙箱 先發現原來好多人單車旅行(因為間間單車店都無紙箱)<br />\n最後我地分別用50同70蚊收購2個紙箱(日本咩紙箱都免費拎 香港真係多得班執紙皮黨唔少)<br />\n我地仲淘寶 每人一個貨架 <br />\n我嘅出發嘅行李如下<br />\n運動衫x3<br />\n單車褲x1<br />\n短褲x1<br />\n長褲x1<br />\n勿3對<br />\n拖鞋x1<br />\n睡袋x1 <br />\n地隻x1<br />\n營骨 (營就我朋友拎)<br />\n整車補胎工具<br />\n仲有其他轉插 iPhone線果d<br />\n我影相用iPhone 同山狗咋 影嘅質素麻麻請見諒<br />\n<br />\n出發前一星期就自己包裝單車 搞左成個下午<br />\n建議大家都自己拆下部車 對了解部車有極大幫助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/235337_806c4c55fc7768d480de8efa5cf75fcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F235337_806c4c55fc7768d480de8efa5cf75fcb.jpg&h=2f7d186f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青蛙包單車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/235419_8b196abf33e13d468a13d653574ac228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F235419_8b196abf33e13d468a13d653574ac228.jpg&h=2a8ae910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行李架 馬鞍袋"},{"pid":"13f0b5d238f28a2ea962400c4fb9354f8be75dd5","tid":254971,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"MORE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />安答好波"},{"pid":"c6c210b7ef9b80c3f3f6f63b05a0841c979444bc","tid":254971,"uid":26310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"劉明"},{"pid":"e97d5470e2563f6bb1d3b61a6f1677c39c8490a5","tid":254971,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <br />\n23 登別去札幌<br />\n24 札幌去稚內<br />\n</blockquote> <br />\n... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168ead8efd8bb17b851ff70c47389b317b476d18","tid":254971,"uid":19109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"a17083f0aeaaa148128f07d0b3cfa7e99c8a6820","tid":254971,"uid":118241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"Day 1 屋企-&gt;香港機場-&gt;福岡機場-&gt;岡垣町(九洲)<br />\n<br />\n因為撘0730機 反正要早起不如唔訓la 玩左成晚fifa 3點半就call Gogo van 出發去機場<br />\n<br />\nHk Express 只要加300蚊就可以運送單車 <br />\n<br />\n上機了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/003321_b89f565555460dad47f728d65622e670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F003321_b89f565555460dad47f728d65622e670.jpg&h=2d4ae040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12點 落機 不過俾日本d入境職員問左好耐 要我地寫第一日留宿嘅地方最後我係google map 亂揾個地方然後抄左個地址就算 搞左一大輪結果最後出境 <br />\n一出黎就見到自己部單車 同埋條運輸帶得返兩件行李<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/003433_5aa54dfa70727d5f840d457d885cdc10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F003433_5aa54dfa70727d5f840d457d885cdc10.jpg&h=04b061b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用左1hr砌返部單車之後就出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/003456_a9dce11a721a6c145a12cde92f513421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F003456_a9dce11a721a6c145a12cde92f513421.jpg&h=8a1ed981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其喺路邊叫日本大媽幫手影<br />\n<br />\n一出機場嘅feel到寒意<br />\n<br />\n下午3點出發了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/003622_4c024e97582faeb12c9f0517735ec346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F003622_4c024e97582faeb12c9f0517735ec346.jpg&h=1e2ff300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay1待續"},{"pid":"bfcbd438c24de1fb6a635b6ab141c07a2c2d018c","tid":254971,"uid":33703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"留名等睇"},{"pid":"80702b73c9eb3da9685d898b0204515cb98aec9b","tid":254971,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:39:19.000Z","msg":"我想環四國，無巴打你志氣咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b66318f8571a956e0d3282ffa5af9b0f8cdd3d","tid":254971,"uid":118241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想環四國，無巴打你志氣咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環四國都唔係易架 大家都一樣enjoy用雙腳去旅行啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ee6c23c017be8f9adb772d59ee890eb013ecf5","tid":254971,"uid":62577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"強帖留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d40fc3cc9cbe985d135b99c68117cf79ed62b","tid":254971,"uid":44833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:51:14.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}